snippet.title: Super Mario 64 3D World
snippet.description:
For more fangames, subscribe to this channel!
https://www.youtube.com/c/KazeEmanuar?sub_confirmation=1

Play with 5 different playable characters -  each with their own unique abilities and voices. Use the dpad on the file select or the act select screen to chose a character.
Mario: can twirl through the air
Luigi: Can jump really high, but he is really slippery
Toad: He's fast, but he can't jump high. Also, he's got a super annoying voice. If you are into that kinda stuff...
Peach: She can float for a few seconds
Rosalina: She can spinjump in mid air

(uses the expansion pack, so enable 8MB ram)
Download:
https://mega.nz/#!LTYFXAjD!OhS170XGFid9dM3vQZj6Nv4sowgJLcAbrvm2gWpSNhw

Source:
https://pastebin.com/krYkg4ew

Shoutouts to AnkleDestroyer for making the custom characters.
( https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTT2HvJ0pGs7O_pBuD2TM8w )

Midi by https://www.youtube.com/user/FacadeMusics/
